---
const tracks = [
  { label: 'RAG', value: 86 },
  { label: 'Agent', value: 78 },
  { label: 'MLOps', value: 64 },
  { label: 'DevTools', value: 82 },
];
---

<section class="radar">
  <div class="radar-visual" aria-label="技能雷达">
    {tracks.map((track, index) => (
      <div class="beam" style={`--angle: ${index * 90}deg; --size: ${track.value}%;`}>
        <span>{track.label}</span>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
  <div class="radar-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">Skill Radar</p>
    <h2>把学习路线收束成可复用能力</h2>
    <p>AI 学习、工程自动化和长期笔记被组织为同一套内容系统：文章负责沉淀，项目负责验证，标签负责串联。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .radar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 320px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 34px;
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 26px;
    background: rgb(9 20 36 / 62%);
  }

  .radar-visual {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 1px solid rgb(40 247 255 / 28%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle, transparent 32%, rgb(40 247 255 / 10%) 33% 34%, transparent 35% 65%, rgb(40 247 255 / 10%) 66% 67%, transparent 68%),
      linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 49%, rgb(40 247 255 / 18%) 50%, transparent 51%),
      linear-gradient(0deg, transparent 49%, rgb(40 247 255 / 18%) 50%, transparent 51%);
  }

  .beam {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: calc(var(--size) / 2);
    height: 2px;
    transform: rotate(var(--angle));
    transform-origin: 0 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-cyan), transparent);
  }

  .beam span {
    position: absolute;
    right: -34px;
    bottom: 8px;
    transform: rotate(calc(var(--angle) * -1));
    color: #dffbff;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .radar-copy h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.7rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .radar-copy p:last-child {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .radar {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .radar-visual {
      max-width: 300px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
